      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "Here's more goals of this change:\r\n- get param by name, like `ctx.Param(\"involves_watchonly\")` and have it with the correct format and make it non-breaking change,\r\n- try to use the default value specified in RPCArg\r\n- support chunked response - don't rely on the return `UniValue`\r\n- this simplifies code review as request.param is no longer used in the new variant\r\n- detect unused arguments\r\n\r\n@MarcoFalke @kallewoof ",
